{
  "stem": "21308.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- but of course, they were still in-- where they had clothes, uniform-- that had this concentration camp stuff, the filthy blue and white striped trousers and jacket and skirts and hats.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of them still had found the-- the whips which their oppressors had used for them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember being shown one of this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, what happened to the chap who had it?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he went, well, you know what that means.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] my abiding memories are, as I went around the various buildings where we put these people in and we centralized the Dutch together-- and they would-- the Dutch from Groningen-- I remember a group of Dutch doctors.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were-- they were carcasses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're living carcasses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but when I went into their hut, as far as they could, they'd kept its-- they'd got it clean.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this group of doctors wanted a picture of Queen Wilhelmina, the Dutch queen, and Montgomery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And believe it or believe it not, I couldn't find a photograph of Montgomery, which is saying something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because he liked publicity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I found a photograph of our royal family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I took it along to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they put it up there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- they were as pleased with that photograph of our king and queen and the two princesses as anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The-- some of them in-- when we actually went in on the 3rd of May, I remember in the shed, which I'll show you a photograph of, which we cleaned up and actually had a ceremonial parade there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they were lying there in this excreta.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Dreadful mess.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Dreadful mess.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And couldn't help themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in the huts where they lay, you know, their-- their bowels reacted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Dreadful.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
